AIM_SCOUT-BRIDGE_TEXTURED			
.................................................................................
A simple map to improve aim & gain skill.	
	
-Scout / Desert Eagle AIM map.		
-Far objectives, you'll need a good aim to hit em.	
-64 units tall craters so you will only see heads everywere.
-32 spawn points. 16 each side.	
-3 ways and a bridge so there is no problem with blocks and you can get em mad..
-GOOD spawn points(behind walls). You'll NEVER join & die.
-Good FPS due to dev textures and simple architectures.	
- Some ramps for bunny hoping and rush enemy's base.		
-NOT HDR, just common lights (sry, my PC SUX). 

ENJOY!				BY DEH0LISE
